The evidence with the title 'NEA - Health Care Facts And Fiction ' says Nationally, 9 million children lack health insurance of any kind. If we do not act, premiums and out - of - pocket costs will continue to skyrocket , and 14,000 Americans will continue to lose their health insurance everysingleday.Insurance for a family of four costs more than $ 12,000 on average, and the cost continues to rise  ... 
